oai_dc:dc.dc:description: The 1916 Middle Tennessee State Normal School football team

Top row (left to right): C. Miles, L. Tackle and Captain; Bomer, L. Guard; Huddleston, Center; Herron, R. Guard; and F. Hill, R. Tackle. Middle row: A. Miles, Coach; Verble, L. End; R. Smith, Quarterback; W. Smith, R. End; and E. Herron, Manager. Bottom row: Cummins, L. Half; H. Ridley, F. Back; and J. Ridley, R. Half.
